    "explanation": "<p>$$\\sqrt{3} \\operatorname{cosec} 20^{\\circ}-\\sec 20^{\\circ}$$</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{aligned}\n& =\\sqrt{3} \\frac{1}{\\sin 20^{\\circ}}-\\frac{1}{\\cos 20^{\\circ}}=\\frac{\\cot 30^{\\circ}}{\\sin 20^{\\circ}}-\\frac{1}{\\cos 20^{\\circ}} \\\\\n& =\\frac{\\cos 30^{\\circ}}{\\sin 30^{\\circ} \\sin 20^{\\circ}}-\\frac{1}{\\cos 20^{\\circ}} \\\\\n& =\\frac{\\cos 30^{\\circ} \\cos 20^{\\circ}-\\sin 30^{\\circ} \\sin 20^{\\circ}}{\\sin 30^{\\circ} \\sin 20^{\\circ} \\cos 20^{\\circ}} \\\\\n& =\\frac{\\cos \\left(30^{\\circ}+20^{\\circ}\\right)}{\\frac{1}{2} \\cdot \\frac{2 \\sin 20^{\\circ} \\cos 20^{\\circ}}{2}}=\\frac{\\cos 50^{\\circ}}{\\frac{1}{4} \\sin 40^{\\circ}}=\\frac{4 \\cos \\left(90^{\\circ}-40^{\\circ}\\right.}{\\sin 40^{\\circ}} \\\\\n& =4 \\frac{\\sin 40^{\\circ}}{\\sin 40^{\\circ}}=4\n\\end{aligned}$$</p>",
